                    ShapeSort © Alex Waugh 1998
                    ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

ShapeSort is a program that tries to identify which shape you have
choosen, by asking yes/no questions for you to answer, until it has
deduced the shape.  It's operation should be fairly self-explanatary.

If you wish to alter any of the pictures, then shift double click on
!Shape 2D (or !Shape 3D) and then open the Pictures directory. All the
pictures are in Draw format. To alter the text, shift double click on
!Shape 2D (or !Shape 3D) and the edit the TreeData file.


